title: 6 Music's Radiohead Playlist
description:
6 Music’s Radiohead Playlist (720p HD)

Radiohead's seminal album OK Computer was released in 1997 and to celebrate its 20th anniversary BBC Radio 6 Music presenter Steve Lamacq looks back across their career.    

Steve Lamacq picks some of the band's most iconic music videos from Fake Plastic Trees to Pyramid Song, plus the ground breaking House of Cards where no cameras or lights where used to make this stunning video. 

They have constantly pushed the boundaries of sound, vision and even releasing techniques and are a tour de force, constantly surprising their fans and the music industry alike.

First broadcast: 17 June 2017
Duration:  1 hour
